#suite s21_extra_math_test

#test s21_add_1
  // -49548
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xc18c, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80000000}};
  // 9246214015.97330
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x3231a592, 0x348f0, 0x0, 0x50000}};
  // 9246164467.97330
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xadd6612, 0x348ef, 0x0, 0x50000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_add(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);


#test s21_add_2
  // -6.749
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x1a5d, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80030000}};
  // 0.5957416215852
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x11ad652c, 0x56b, 0x0, 0xd0000}};
  // -6.1532583784148
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xabcc6ed4, 0x37f6, 0x0, 0x800d0000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_add(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

#test s21_add_27
  // 6654
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x19fe, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // 1226097.3676
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0xdacf9c6c, 0x2, 0x0, 0x40000}};
  // 1232751.3676

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x11515e4, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // -87233.2320
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x33febc20, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80040000}};
  // 18071842.7680
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x13a85e20, 0x2a, 0x0, 0x40000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_add(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

#test s21_add_107
  // 0.8409
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x20d9, 0x0, 0x0, 0x40000}};
  // -8902104518371023
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0xb99226cf, 0x1fa06a, 0x0, 0x80000000}};
  // -8902104518371022.1591
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xdd0bd517, 0xd36a48f0, 0x4, 0x80040000}};

#test s21_add_215
  // -0.07
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x7, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80020000}};
  // -4137172

  // -4137172.07

#test s21_add_348
  // 0.606918932548218
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x5361ca7a, 0x227fd, 0x0, 0xf0000}};
  // -2471385591.66163

#test s21_sub_77
  // 7607168941956.88

#test s21_sub_134
  // -396865222484669231764.600
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xb5eb9478, 0x1b588fbd, 0x540a, 0x80030000}};
  // -51596558124218.66091034932565
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x967b7555, 0xe25acdc, 0x10abf79e, 0x800e0000}};
  // -396865170888111107545.93908965
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xfa91a8e5, 0x4db91157, 0x803beae2, 0x80080000}};

#test s21_sub_187
  // 21035907308194
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xcdc85aa2, 0x1321, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // -5572351086095079497.738519868
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x6518853c, 0xab78d117, 0x1201573d, 0x80090000}};
  // 5572372122002387691.738519868
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x5810593c, 0x75474e1, 0x12015bb2, 0x90000}};

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xe, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80010000}};
  // 78056579507
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x2c88e1b3, 0x12, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // -78056579508.4
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xbd58d10c, 0xb5, 0x0, 0x80010000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_sub(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x965b, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // 490.183
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x77ac7, 0x0, 0x0, 0x30000}};
  // 38000.817
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x243d8b1, 0x0, 0x0, 0x30000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_sub(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

#test s21_sub_325
  // -814391225
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x308a9fb9, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80000000}};
  // -743520557.8023695709
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x6e1af55d, 0x672f2814, 0x0, 0x800a0000}};
  // -70870667.1976304291

  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);

#test s21_mul_30
  // 1.41881
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x22a39, 0x0, 0x0, 0x50000}};
  // -444449549041116236.220029

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xf65b5166, 0xf2e299b9, 0x4, 0x800e0000}};
  // -7817
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x1e89, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80000000}};
  // 7136037399.20882012291990
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x8a688396, 0x89480f63, 0x971c, 0xe0000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_mul(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xcc17e10a, 0x7e676558, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // 0.596
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x254, 0x0, 0x0, 0x30000}};
  // 5428582681247714110.280
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x2797eb48, 0x48b7f2bb, 0x126, 0x30000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_mul(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  // 1.20280707513292

  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);

  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

#test s21_mul_330
  // -595402.4150841837047939
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x30815083, 0xc4af0b6b, 0x142, 0x80100000}};
  // -0.874
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x36a, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80030000}};
  // 520381.7107835765579898686
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x997cdf3e, 0x7d9cfbf3, 0x44df3, 0x130000}};
  s21_decimal result;

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xcc, 0x0, 0x0, 0x0}};
  // -2285855485135467438962
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0xd1bde372, 0xea9e0cbf, 0x7b, 0x80000000}};
  // -466314518967635357548248
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x23513ed8, 0xf5f228db, 0x62be, 0x80000000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_mul(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

#test s21_mul_384
  // 3854620478494959.8
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0xaba5795e, 0x88f191, 0x0, 0x10000}};
  // 4366.81689489553296
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0xd5f13790, 0x60f67ae, 0x0, 0xe0000}};
  // 16832421828902093835.274068895

  // 19412833855494948055
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xb87404d7, 0xd683d89, 0x1, 0x0}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_mul(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x3e804a1b, 0x6a61c708, 0x32386, 0x80000000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  // overflow
  int check = 1; // Результат слишком велик или положительная бесконечность.
  int return_value = s21_mul(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, check);

#test s21_div_2
  // 47142453.2758432798261901917
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x6237fa5d, 0x210504e0, 0x185f407, 0x130000}};
  // -3.2
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x20, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80010000}};
  // -14732016.648701024945684434906
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xfd554fda, 0xc7dcd863, 0x2f9a09de, 0x80150000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_div(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  int return_value = s21_div(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

#test s21_div_57
  // 134455.388104
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x4e2a67c8, 0x1f, 0x0, 0x60000}};
  // 318.0555390205396762710568
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0xc75228, 0x40d0f723, 0x2a182, 0x160000}};
  // 422.74185357079104093649963097

#test s21_div_178
  // -16662175289960.28510330
  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x8168707a, 0x5369ce9f, 0x5a, 0x80080000}};
  // -441134.607426647912

  // 37771181.425005019872649491954

#test s21_div_261

#test s21_div_465
  // 38937554031410

  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x39f9a, 0x0, 0x0, 0x60000}};
  // -25565280903585328450.551249442
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0xd1c57a22, 0xcb20d3a5, 0x529b1ace, 0x80090000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_div(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);

  // -5043681269.984341423

  // -367
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0x16f, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80000000}};
  // 13743000.735652156465940054496
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x6170c1e0, 0xb404c36d, 0x2c67f19a, 0x150000}};

#test s21_div_499

  s21_decimal dec_1 = {{0x5c452b8e, 0x9f8663a0, 0x80e9ee87, 0x80000}};
  // -2.45
  s21_decimal dec_2 = {{0xf5, 0x0, 0x0, 0x80020000}};
  // -162844438359717285551.56149348
  s21_decimal dec_check = {{0x4a3b9464, 0x3be342c9, 0x349e2d1d, 0x80080000}};
  s21_decimal result;
  int return_value = s21_div(dec_1, dec_2, &result);
  ck_assert_int_eq(return_value, 0);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[0], result.bits[0]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[1], result.bits[1]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[2], result.bits[2]);
  ck_assert_uint_eq(dec_check.bits[3], result.bits[3]);
